"     <br>",
"      &bull; Martin A, Young C, Leckman JF, Mukonoweshuro C, Rosenheck R, Leslie D. Age effects on antidepressant-induced manic conversion. Arch Pediatr Adolesc Med 2004;158:773-780.",
"      <br>",
"       &Delta; Boyer EW, Shannon M. The serotonin syndrome. N Engl J Med 2005;352:1112-20.",
"      </br>",
"     </br>",
"    </div>",
"    <div class=\"reference\">",
